{
  "texts": [
    "Mukund et al.",
    "[32] apply the CRF approach for the identification of three NE types namely, person, organization, and location.",
    "Words with POS information are used by following the bootstrapping methods to increase the size of training data.",
    "A four-stage model is adopted in which the first three stages are trained for the CRF approach and one stage uses the rule-based approach to maximize the performance of NEs tagging.",
    "For all stages of training, unigram and bigram features for the tags and words are used."
  ]
}